Source: conpalette
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: nick black <nick.black@sprezzatech.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), perl
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: http://search.cpan.org/~hinrik/App-ConPalette-0.1.5/

Package: conpalette
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl
Description: Utility to change the console palette
 conpalette uses the Linux console's escape codes to change the console
 palette. Includes 'konsole', 'rxvt', 'sinclair', 'tango-dark',
 'tango-light', and 'xterm'.

Package: conpalette-udeb
Architecture: all
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl
Description: Utility to change the console palette
 conpalette uses the Linux console's escape codes to change the console
 palette. Includes 'konsole', 'rxvt', 'sinclair', 'tango-dark',
 'tango-light', and 'xterm'.
